data.description: Nestled on a sprawling acre of land, this unique modern bungalow offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. With two bedrooms and two bathrooms (master bath remodeled in 2023), this charming  home provides ample space for relaxation and privacy. The BONUS ROOM added in 2023 provides endless possibilities for customization, whether it be a home office, craft room, reading nook, or home gym! What sets this property apart is the inclusion of a tornado shelter, providing peace of mind during stormy weather. Don't forget the detached 2 car garage with ample storage or work space. Step outside onto the large covered deck, an oasis for relaxation and outdoor gatherings and take in the breathtaking views of the Ozarks! Want some exercise? You're just 8-10 minutes from Empire Park or Shadow Rock Park where you'll find paved walking trails and a manicured disc golf course!  Whether you're looking to relax in the comfort of this charming bungalow or enjoy the vast outdoor space, this property truly offers the best of both worlds.
